{
  "stem": "14928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You could have another name and live, you know, not as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another time he came in-- came in and said to me, all this war is because of your Jewish relatives in America-- all because of your Jewish relatives in America.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They want war.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't want war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't pay attention.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't discuss.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just-- he told me I should walk out when he comes in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when he started talking, I just walked out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the idea at that time came to me when he said about, you know, I should be Katya, not Peshe.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this is when I got the idea when we got into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one day also came an order that Jews can't-- can't work anymore in the barracks mixed with German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, uh, we couldn't work there anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All the-- about the time when we still worked, they came in, soldiers, older people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were high-ranking people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They came in from Rowne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Rowne is a big city in Ukraine, where there were a lot of Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they liquidated Rowne.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There couldn't be-- there weren't any Jews anymore in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And those people, the older people, saved some Jewish girls in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they placed them in farms, in big farms around where Germans were, their friends, older people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Mostly older people were managing farms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They couldn't go on the front.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those men-- they must have been in their 70s or 65 or something like this-- used to ask when we have to go back and we lose the war, will you let us change clothes?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we didn't know what to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were afraid even to discuss things like this with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know who they are.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
